                            </h4>
											<div id="tab-3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
												<p>
													<ul>
														<li>Valid Trade Licence / Business Licence (should not be expired).</li>
														<li>Passport/Emirates ID of the authorised signatory. (should not be expired).</li>
														<li>Proof of authorisation for the authorised signatory.</li>
														<li>Monthly turnover declaration for the specified periods that is signed and stamped by the authorised signatory on the entity’s printed letterhead, and supporting financial documents such as: invoices, purchase orders, title deeds, and lease agreements..</li>
														<li>A copy of the legislation that establishes the entity in case the registration request was in relation to a federal / local government entity</li>
														<li>Bank Account details</li>
														<li>Custom registration documents in each Emirate, if applicable.</li>
														<li>The estimated imports value of one year to each GCC countries.</li>
														<li>The estimated exports value  for one year for each GCC countries.</li>


													</ul>
